"title": "4858: whirlwind",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4858: whirlwind",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A violent wind, often associated with the presence and activity of God.</p>\n<h2>The presence of God in whirlwinds</h2>\n<h3>In replying to Job</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:1\">JOB 38:1</a></strong></p>\n<h3>In the forces of nature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:18\">PSA 77:18</a></strong></p>\n<h3>In taking Elijah up to heaven</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:11\">2KI 2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:1\">2KI 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:3\">NAM 1:3</a></p>\n<h2>Whirlwinds as symbols of disaster or divine judgment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:24\">ISA 40:24</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:19\">JER 23:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:27\">PRO 1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:28\">ISA 5:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa21:1\">ISA 21:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:15\">ISA 66:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:13\">JER 4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos4:19\">HOS 4:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos8:7\">HOS 8:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:14\">ZEC 7:14</a></p>",
